COMMENTS="WM/DE integration:
		1-) Add ConsoleKit.tcz to onboot.lst
		2-) For flwm_topside:
			\$ echo start-desktop > /etc/sysconfig/desktop
		    For compiz:
			\$ echo \"start-desktop compiz\" > /etc/sysconfig/desktop
		    For others:
			\$ echo \"start-desktop <xxx>\" > /etc/sysconfig/desktop
			where <xxx> is a window manager or a desktop session manager

		3-) Add etc/sysconfig/desktop to backup (/opt/.filetool.lst) for persistency
			\$ echo etc/sysconfig/desktop >> /opt/.filetool.lst
		4-) Backup and reboot
			\$ filetool.sh -b && sudo reboot"
